Posts.Content: Jan 28, 2008 04:28PM youngsurvivor wrote: I am from Florida and did not get treatment in Miami.  However, in Boca Raton, FL you will find an excellent breast cancer oncologist.  He is part of the Lynn Regional Cancer Center and his name is Dr. Charles Vogel.  He is very well-known in the circle of Breast Cancer Oncologists from all over the world.  If his office cannot give you help, perhaps they can give you someone in Sylvester.  Good luck!  Their office number is (561)883-7600.
